author: Muscat Daily
title: Oman- OTE recalls Corvettes
text:
(MENAFN - Muscat Daily) Oman Trading Establishment (OTE) in cooperation with the Public Authority for Consumer Protection (PACP) has launched a recall of Chevloret Corvettes 2014 and 2015 models. A release said that automatic transmission in these cars are as per US standards and not GCC  specifications.
These transmissions will have to be reprogrammed to meet GCC standards it said. Cars with the following chassis numbers have been recalled: u1G1Y92D76E5114146 to 1G1Y92D70E5131315 and u1G1Y92D7XF5104141 to 1G1Y92D72E5123202.
